The <code><strong>CanvasRenderingContext2D</strong></code> interface, part of the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API">Canvas API</a>, provides the 2D rendering context for the drawing surface of a <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas" title="Use the HTML &lt;canvas&gt; element with either the canvas scripting API or the WebGL API to draw graphics and animations."><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> element. It is used for drawing shapes, text, images, and other objects.